data.description: Price reduced! Don't Miss this one of a kind larger unit in this community. Features spacious open floorplan, 2 master suites, 2 balcony's and storage, storage, storage! Elevator access in the building. Close to I-15, I-215, Jordan River Parkway and downtown in just minutes. Low maintenance, secure building entrance, secure heated underground parking (one space assigned to each unit) and pet friendly. Lot's of amenities within the HOA. New water heater, disposal and carpet 2023. Newer furnace/a/c, stainless steel appliances and refrigerator included. Rooms are spacious with three bathrooms, additional private storage closet located outside the unit. Additional unassigned guest parking outside. ADA features and accessibility. Information provided as a courtesy, Buyer and agent to verify all information provided.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
